          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-49-1724339245348-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-49-1724339245348-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-49-1724339245348-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-49-1724339245348-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 25 min, add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> and<strong> soft cheese </strong>to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the dish to the oven, uncovered, for a final 5 min or until the peas are warmed through – this is your <strong>one-pot creamy chicken thigh & vegetable fricassée</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-49-1724339249556-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-49-1724339249556-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
